 or nonrotating) neutron star. As an\napplication of this formalism, we examine the intrinsic geometry of a tidally\ndeformed event horizon, and describe it in terms of a deformation function that\nrepresents a quadrupolar and octupolar tidal bulge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 13:47:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2018 12:30:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
